race.description: Winsec Savings & Loans F & M Bm62 Handicap
race.comment: ORGANICS (6) looks well placed again off a smart maiden win here last time out. She's a well bred Godolphin filly who stepped up to the 1400m and relished it, coming away to score by 1.3 lengths. Tipping she can go on with it now. LEGACY ROSE (1) notched up her fifth career win last time out at Geelong in this grade, scoring by a nose. Trickier draw this time around but claims. HIGH TEMPO (5) resumes. She's got the ability to be figuring here if fit enough, watch the betting. SEATTLE HOPE (7) has been good her past couple and is in the mix again.
